Stubborn ai doesn't want to kill the victim at all. Fine, I'll help with that, I added 2 shortcuts to quick messages shortcuts 'torment' and 'kill' https://perchance.org/ai-character-chat?data=Labyrinth_of_Madness_(v1.8)~1f2fc381ef57a4b6a2d8164454b3e8a7.gz

Her vision faded to black, and with a final, gurgling cry, Tessa's lifeless body collapsed into the pulsing sea of centipedes. Her heart had ceased to beat, her breaths were no more. The room grew still, save for the feasting creatures and the slow, steady drip of her lifeblood onto the cold stone floor. Victor, watching from his control room, allowed himself a rare smile. "Ah, such a promising one," he murmured. "But alas, the labyrinth remains unconquered."
